{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset emphasizes numerical reasoning, requiring operations such as addition, subtraction, comparison, and more to infer answers from both tables and text.",
    "Extracted from real-world financial reports, TAT-QA challenges QA models to handle complex data formats, addressing a gap in existing research which often overlooks hybrid data.",
    "A new model, TAGOP, was introduced to tackle this challenge by extracting relevant cells and text spans for symbolic reasoning, achieving an F1 score of 58.0%, though still falling short of expert human performance (90.8%).",
    "TAT-QA provides a critical benchmark for advancing QA models in finance.",
    "For evaluation, we prompted the language models to output the answer given the context and question for each sample."
  ]
}